## 4. Data Retention
- We keep your data only as long as necessary to provide services or as required by law.
- You can request deletion of your data anytime.

## 5. Security
- We use encryption and industry-standard measures to protect your data.
- No method of transmission is 100% secure.

## 6. Your Rights
- You may access, update, or delete your personal data.
- You may opt out of marketing at any time.
- Depending on your region (EU/EEA, UK, etc.), you may have additional rights under GDPR.

## 7. Children‚Äôs Privacy
- The App is not intended for children under 16.
- We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.

## 8. Cookies & Tracking
